Package: duckbotos-kiosk-hermes
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: duckbotos-kiosk,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Pre-configure DuckBotOS kiosk for Hermes dashboard
 Configures /etc/duckbotos/kiosk-mode to load the Hermes Web Dashboard
 (http://localhost:9119) when the kiosk starts.
 .
 This package conflicts with duckbotos-kiosk-openclaw — installing one
 deconfigures the other.
Conflicts: duckbotos-kiosk-openclaw
